text: Gunnar Jervill (born 23 November 1945 in Gothenburg) is a Swedish archer. Gunnar competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics and at the 1976 Summer Olympics.Gunnar JervillGunnar JERVILL ==References== Category:1945 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish archers Category:Olympic silver medalists for Sweden Category:Sportspeople from Gothenburg
